_sText:
This is my entry for the fall 2020 KSF mapping contest. I didn't have too much time, but wanted to get something done for it.

Hope some of you will enjoy!

-----------------------------------------------------------
-> Tier 2
-> 3 Stages
-> 1 Bonus
-----------------------------------------------------------
Map is supposed to be themed towards arcade games.

Therefore:

Stage 1 is Pacman
Stage 2 Mario
Stage 3 Tetris

Bonus Donkey Kong
